{"tid":1976098,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【獨家】國泰關閉所有美國機組人員基地　空服員全炒","createTime":"2020-04-17T04:07:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T04:42:06.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ab7080dbe33488bf49ad75eb4d52a25a787daa8c","tid":1976098,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:07:13.000Z","msg":"國泰（293）機艙服務部總經理毛潔瓊（Jeanette Mao）向以美國為基地全體機組人員發內部信，宣佈美國的機組人員基地（cabin crew bases）將全面關閉，以美國為基地的機組人員將被裁員。<br />\n<br />\n毛潔瓊在信中指，關閉所有美國的機組人員基地是一個非常艱難的決定，有關決定已通知美國空中服務員工會(Association of Flight Attendants-CWA (AFA-CWA))。信中又附上裁員通知，據當地法規，裁員需於60日前通知僱員，因此以美國為基地的空服員最後上班日期為今年6月20日。毛指，目前僅餘的客運需求已消失，集團的客運機隊幾乎停飛，4月國泰前往美國的航班僅餘下每周兩班前往洛杉磯的航班。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，目前國泰於三藩市、洛杉磯均有聘用以美國為基地的機組人員。信中未有交代受影響員工數目。本報正就事件向國泰查詢。<br />\n<br />\n據國泰2019年年報，國泰航空連同其附屬公司在全球僱用逾3.42萬名員工，香港佔約2萬，其餘為香港以外僱員，惟未有細分不同地區僱員數目。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200417/large/1587095395_87bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200417%2Flarge%2F1587095395_87bd.jpg&h=61146366&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200417/5YBM2OMEABOTAR43MNO67M6U7M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200417%2F5YBM2OMEABOTAR43MNO67M6U7M%2F&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU94vgSq%2BgcR%2FX%2FBaLnjou7zI%3D&h=f4260170\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200417%2F5YBM2OMEABOTAR43MNO67M6U7M%2F&h=f196bd7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200417/5YBM2OMEABOTAR43MNO67M6U7M/</a>"},{"pid":"c8efecd870380687634b5100e41f002657c024a8","tid":1976098,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:28:05.000Z","msg":"mao<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39011ba0b5d692d9a409331ac322afbe14666d08","tid":1976098,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9afcb56488fae4a15de4d1d24f668882e80ef70d","tid":1976098,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"大家準備好文革同上村下鄉未"}]}